                    <li>Search for DEMO-SP001</li>
                    <li>Verify audit log entry shows "Sponsor Updated" with old and new values</li>
                </ol>

                <h6 class="mt-3">Expected Results:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Admin can directly edit and save sponsor records</li>
                    <li>Changes are applied immediately (no change request)</li>
                    <li>Success message and redirect work correctly</li>
                    <li>Audit log captures the change with old/new values</li>
                </ul>

                <h6 class="mt-3">Pass Criteria:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Admin can update sponsor fields directly</li>
                    <li>Changes are saved immediately</li>
                    <li>Audit log entry is created with change details</li>
                    <li>Admissions user cannot use this workflow (must submit change request)</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mt-3">
                    <span class="badge bg-danger">Priority: Critical</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-warning">Estimated Time: 10 minutes</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
