                <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i> UT07: Submit Sponsor Profile Change Request
                <span class="badge bg-warning float-end">Admissions</span>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="ut07" class="collapse">
            <div class="card-body">
                <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Verify Admissions user can submit change requests for Admin approval.</p>
                <p><strong>Actors:</strong> Admissions</p>
                <p><strong>Demo Accounts:</strong> demo.admissions@ism.edu.ph</p>
                
                <h6 class="mt-3">Test Steps:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Login as Admissions user</li>
                    <li>Navigate to <code>/Sponsors/Index</code></li>
                    <li>Search for DEMO-SP002 (Asian Development Bank)</li>
                    <li>Click "Edit"</li>
                    <li>Change Billing Address to "Updated Address, Makati City, Philippines"</li>
