                    <li>Admissions user cannot directly update sponsor fields</li>
                    <li>Edit action creates a change request instead</li>
                    <li>Change request shows in Dashboard "Pending Requests"</li>
                    <li>Admissions user cannot approve their own requests</li>
                </ul>

                <h6 class="mt-3">Pass Criteria:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Admissions user can submit change requests</li>
                    <li>Change request is created with correct details (sponsor, field, old/new values)</li>
                    <li>Change request appears in Dashboard pending list</li>
                    <li>Admissions user cannot approve requests (no "Approve" button visible)</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mt-3">
                    <span class="badge bg-danger">Priority: Critical</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-warning">Estimated Time: 10 minutes</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
